<!-- 3 methods for adding cssss
*Inline css:Directly in the html element
*Internal css:Using<STYLE.>tags within a single document in head tag
*ExternalCSS: Linking an external .css file
ctrl U for html code
css  is strictly for styling and presentation
-->
